---
// Impact — How embodied AI affects humanity
---

<section class="section impact-section" id="impact">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-label animate-on-scroll">Impact</div>
      <h2 class="section-title animate-on-scroll">Shaping the Future</h2>
      <p class="section-desc animate-on-scroll">
        Embodied AI is not just a technical challenge — it has profound implications for how we live, work, and age.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="impact-grid">
      <article class="impact-card glass-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="impact-icon">🏥</div>
        <h3>Healthcare & Eldercare</h3>
        <p>Assistive robots can help an aging population with daily tasks, rehabilitation exercises, and companionship — extending independent living and easing caregiver burden in societies facing demographic shifts.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="impact-card glass-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="impact-icon">🏭</div>
        <h3>Manufacturing & Logistics</h3>
        <p>Flexible, adaptive robots can handle small-batch production and unpredictable warehouse conditions — making automation accessible beyond large factories to small businesses and diverse supply chains.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="impact-card glass-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="impact-icon">🌾</div>
        <h3>Agriculture & Environment</h3>
        <p>Autonomous agents can monitor crops, manage invasive species, and operate in hazardous environments — enabling precision agriculture and environmental monitoring at scales humans alone cannot achieve.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="impact-card glass-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="impact-icon">🔬</div>
        <h3>Scientific Discovery</h3>
        <p>Robots that can manipulate lab equipment, run experiments, and explore extreme environments accelerate discovery in chemistry, biology, and space exploration — doing the work that is slow, dangerous, or impossible for humans.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="impact-card glass-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="impact-icon">🏠</div>
        <h3>Daily Life</h3>
        <p>Household robots that cook, clean, and organize could reclaim hours of domestic labor — reshaping how people spend their time and enabling greater focus on creative, social, and professional pursuits.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="impact-card glass-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="impact-icon">⚖️</div>
        <h3>Challenges & Responsibility</h3>
        <p>Embodied AI raises important questions about safety, employment, equity, and accountability. Building these systems responsibly — with human oversight and inclusive design — is as important as building them well.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Quote -->
<section class="section quote-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="quote-content">
      <blockquote class="quote-block animate-on-scroll">
        <p>"The next leap in AI will not come from bigger models alone, but from machines that learn through physical interaction — seeing, touching, and reasoning about the world as humans do."</p>
        <footer>
          <span class="quote-line"></span>
          <span>EAI LAB</span>
        </footer>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .impact-section {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto 3.5rem;
  }

  .section-header .section-label {
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .section-header .section-label::before {
    display: none;
  }

  .impact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .impact-card {
    padding: 1.75rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .impact-icon {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .impact-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .impact-card p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Quote */
  .quote-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .quote-content {
    max-width: 780px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .quote-block {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }

  .quote-block p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .quote-block footer {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .quote-line {
    width: 24px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 1px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .impact-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .impact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .quote-block { padding: 2rem 1.25rem; }
    .quote-block p { font-size: 1rem; }
  }
</style>
